SUMMARY:Notes of Honey: Michael Zeligs and Cedar Roots Live
DESCRIPTION:Come see our live music show in Sonoma County! Free to enter\, $4 Cacao Doubleshots available. Michael Zeligs is a Stanford-trained composer and Sonoma county yogi-songwriter having released four LP’s of eclectic American Kirtan\, previously leading poetic song weaving music circles. Now he will present his new body of work\, in the genre of ‘vintage soul’\, with Kim Atkinson on drums. Michael’s Prior Music https://open.spotify.com/artist/7FMvM52G5eOgE8j9KPcoSo\n‘cedar roots’ is the opening live music act / Ecstatic Dance DJ hybrid\, their vocalist was raised in whales\, and they are based in Edmonton Canada\, this is one of a limited set of stops here for them on their Notes of Honey West Coast tour. They have just been performing all over the Big island on the island of Hawaii\, and now they are taking their smooth vocals and soothing fresh beats to us\, to help warm up the night. Cedar Roots Music: https://open.spotify.com/artist/4lCc8SfyJy1YThKV4o0sF9?si=ddh2FCTdT32-6B4dkiLfAA
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/notes-of-honey-michael-zeligs-and-cedar-roots-live/
LOCATION:Sebastopol Grange Hall\, 6000 Sebastopol Ave\, Sebastopol\, 95472
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.40844;-122.80724
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Sebastopol Grange Hall 6000 Sebastopol Ave Sebastopol 95472;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=6000 Sebastopol Ave:geo:-122.80724,38.40844
END:VEVENT
