SUMMARY:Michelle Lambert at Adobe Road Winery
DESCRIPTION:Join us Thursday night for indoor live music at Adobe Road Winery! Sip on award-winning wines while enjoying talented local musicians in a warm and inviting atmosphere. Choose from wines by the glass or bottle and discover new favorites. Reserve your spot on Tock and make it a memorable night of great music\, fine wine\, and good company! \nRising star\, Michelle Lambert\, brings a world of experience when she steps up to the microphone. This Pop singer/songwriter has toured from coast to coast making waves all over the country from the Great American Music Hall in San Francisco to the Bridgestone Arena in Nashville. Michelle’s 2021 single\, Come to Me\, has caught the attention of the press and reached #1 on Indie Radio for 4 consecutive weeks.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/michelle-lambert-at-adobe-road-winery-4/
LOCATION:Adobe Road Winery\, 6 Petaluma Blvd N\, Petaluma\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
