SUMMARY:Chris Murphy at Rio Nido Roadhouse
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an unforgettable evening with Chris Murphy\, a dynamic violinist known for blending classical technique with modern energy and improvisation. \nFrom soulful melodies to high-energy loops\, Chris transforms the violin into a full-band experience—layering sound in real time and taking listeners on a genre-crossing journey through classical\, folk\, rock\, and beyond. \nWhether you’re here for dinner\, drinks\, or the music\, this is a performance that pulls you in and doesn’t let go.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/chris-murphy-at-rio-nido-roadhouse/
