SUMMARY:The Grey Fox Trio at Cloverdale Arts Alliance
DESCRIPTION:On the heels of her sold-out performance at Americana Night\, Sarah Ryan (of the Real Sarahs) returns to the Cloverdale Arts Alliance Gallery for a very special edition of The Jazz Club. \nFor over a decade\, Sarah has shared her soulful voice and original music on stages throughout Northern California. A celebrated name in the West Coast Americana scene\, she recently returned to her jazz roots with her band\, the Grey Fox Trio. \nJoining Sarah are Dan McDonnell on guitar and Nathan McMath on clarinet and saxophone. \nDoors open at 7:00 pm. Music starts at 7:30 pm.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-grey-fox-trio-at-cloverdale-arts-alliance/
