SUMMARY:Sacred 3: Homage to Mother Earth Art Opening
DESCRIPTION:Artist Mary Vaughan hosts 12 Artists at Backstreet Gallery (Santa Rosa) to help her pay homage to Earth Day Month.\nEach artist will display 3 pieces from their body of work that honors the planet. Guest Artists are: Chris Beards\,\nLisa Beerntsen\, Ken Berman\, Rachel Dufour\, Cathy Hazel\, Corrine Haverinen\, Karen Ingalls\, Diana Majumdar\, Nick Mancillas\,\nLinda Schroeter\, Tony Speirs & Mario Uribe.
